channel.title: Runescape Map Editor - peterbjorn's [question]
channel.description:
I'm using the map editor by peterbjorn to edit my map and add new areas.
my main problem is that i can't integrate the edited maps with MY client
if i copy my cache and replace the map editor's cache, it gives an error.
if i edit using their cache and try integrating it into my client, it doesnt run.
so how do I integrate my new map?
are there specific files that only need to be copied?
